!!!HTML5
%html
  %head
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  %body
    %h1= "Hi #{@writer.name}!"
    %p  
      The deadline for submission to 
      = "Volume #{@current_issue.volume},"
      = "Issue #{@current_issue.issue}"
      is 
      %strong= @current_issue.submission_deadline.to_s(:pretty)
    %p 
      Why am I telling you this? You said you'd write something for us! You claimed the following:
      %ul 
        - @assignments.each do |a|
          %li= a.idea.headline
    %p
      Don't let us down, you're our only hope!
    %p 
      Send your submissions to 
      %a{:href => "mailto:submissions@chicagoshadydealer.com"} submissions@chicagoshadydealer.com
      by 
      %strong= @current_issue.submission_deadline.to_s(:pretty)
